        {
            "title": "惠譽下調菲律賓信用評級展望至「負面」 能源衝擊與投資放緩成主要挑戰",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PcOOvAm5Erp02uJBNduy7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/cc33c9b7428ecdd674602e1a3dea1225\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%83%A0%E8%AD%BD%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E8%B3%93%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E5%B1%95%E6%9C%9B%E8%87%B3-%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E8%88%87%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9%E6%88%90%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0-060002305.html",
